{"article_id":"xGIN5GNMLUhtH326","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Obama administration promised to have the Obamacare website working smoothly by Saturday ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"but even President Obama knows","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"this latest deadline is another target","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"that his team is likely to miss .","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"Only about 25,000 Americans were able to enroll on the federal government ' s HealthCare.gov website in October ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"when most people instead encountered computer errors .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"although Mr. Obama and his top advisers vowed to fix the problems by the end of November ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"they have retreated from that pledge in favor of a scaled-back promise by Health and Human Service Secretary Kathleen Sebelius","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"that the website will be working for \" most users \" by Saturday ' s deadline .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"This week , administration officials acknowledged","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"they are holding back on a marketing campaign for the program","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"because they don ' t want too many users to visit the flawed site .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"And HHS also revealed this week","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that the Spanish-language version of HealthCare.gov still isn ' t ready to enroll people ;","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"HHS is postponing that service again until sometime in December .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"The administration also Wednesday announced another major delay ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"putting off by one year the online program","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"that lets small businesses shop for plans through the federal Obamacare marketplace .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"The developments are the latest in a series of downsized goals , broken promises and delays for Obamacare","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"since the program became law of the land in 2010 .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"If there has been a hallmark of Obamacare so far ,","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"it has been watching Mr. Obama ' s optimistic assurances crumble later under the weight of reality .","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"\" The administration completely oversold what it was going to be , in terms of all dessert and no spinach , \"","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"said Paul Howard , a specialist on health-care policy at the nonprofit Manhattan Institute .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"Throughout the president ' s re-election campaign in 2012 , Mr. Obama trumpeted the signature achievement of his first term","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"and told voters","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"that he was trustworthy above all else .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" You do want to be able to trust your president , \"","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Mr. Obama told supporters in Ohio a few days before Election Day .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"\" You want to know","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that your president means what he says ,","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"and says what he means .","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"And after four years as president , you know me .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"You know","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"where I stand .","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"You know","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"I tell the truth . \"","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"Those words stand in stark contrast to Mr. Obama ' s now-infamous broken pledge ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"repeatedly made","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"without qualification ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that \" if you like your health-insurance plan ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"you can keep your plan. \"","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"By last month ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"with more than 3.5 million people being forced out of their old insurance policies by Obamacare ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"the president admitted","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that his promise wasn ' t true for many people .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Behind the scenes , he reportedly berated his staff","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"for allowing him to boast in public","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that buying health insurance would be as easy as shopping on Amazon.com .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"In an interview with Barbara Walters","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"to be broadcast Friday night on ABC ' s \" 20/20 \" show ,","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Mr. Obama said","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"his team is looking into why he was kept in the dark about the website ' s problems .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"\" We ' re evaluating","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"why it is exactly","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"that I didn ' t know soon enough","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that [ it ] wasn ' t going to work the way","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"it needed to , \"","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"Mr. Obama said .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"\" But my priority now has been to just make sure","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"that it works . \"","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"But even the president ' s apology was a bit of misdirection .","depth":5},{"id":63,"text":"Mr. Obama knew as early as February 2010 ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"one month before he signed the law ,","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that millions of Americans wouldn ' t be able to keep their health insurance .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"At a health care summit with congressional Republicans at Blair House on Feb. 25 , 2010 , House Majority Leader Eric Cantor , Virginia Republican ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"who was House minority whip at the time ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"voiced concern to the president","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"that \" between eight million and nine million people may very well lose the coverage","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"that they have","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"because of the construct of this bill . \"","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"you can answer the question in the positive","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to say","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"that people will be able to maintain their coverage ,","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"people will be able to see the doctors","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"they want ,","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"in the kind of bill","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"that you are proposing , \"","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"Mr. Cantor told Mr. Obama .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"The president replied","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"that a relatively small portion of the population would be affected ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"and they would be better off under Obamacare .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Mr. Obama told Mr. Cantor ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"\" The eight to nine million people","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"you refer to","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"that might have to change their coverage","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"- keep in mind","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"out of the 300 million Americans","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"that we are talking about -","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"would be folks","depth":16},{"id":92,"text":"who","depth":18},{"id":93,"text":"the Congressional Budget Office estimates","depth":18},{"id":94,"text":"would find the deal in the exchange better .","depth":17},{"id":95,"text":"So , yes , they would change coverage","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"because they got more choice and competition . \"","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"Those promises ,","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Mr. Howard said ,","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"\" were papered over \" later with regulations","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"requiring more expensive coverage for many .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"\" The administration had to require tight grandfathering of current plans","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"to move people into the exchanges ,","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"which means cancellations , \"","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"Mr. Howard said .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Within six months of his second inauguration , Mr. Obama had broken his own law ,","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"delaying the crucial employer mandate portion of Obamacare by a full year until 2015 .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"The administration cited confusion by businesses","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"about how to report employee insurance information to the Internal Revenue Service .","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"The president told supporters in Southern California this week","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"that he ' ll never back down from making sure","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"the law works .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"\" We are going to continue to implement the health care law , \"","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"Mr. Obama said .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"\" The product is good .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"People want it .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"And we should not live in a country","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"where people are going bankrupt","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"just because they get sick .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"And anybody","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"who is going to keep on pushing against that ,","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"they will meet my resistance ,","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"because I am willing to fix any problems","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"that there are ,","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"but I ' m not going to abandon people","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"to make sure","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"that they ' ve got health insurance in this country . \"","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"With the faulty website preventing many people from enrolling ,","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"health care analysts say","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"the next problem for Obamacare could be the failure","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"to bring young , healthy people into the program .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"Obamacare needs people","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"who don ' t require much medical care","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"to still be paying premiums ,","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"to offset the costs of older , sicker people","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"who place greater demands on the system .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"\" They have assumed wrongly","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"that the plans","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"they ' re trying to sell through the exchanges","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"are going to be attractive to relatively healthy Americans , \"","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"said James Capretta , a public policy specialist at the right-leaning American Enterprise Institute .","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"\" I just think","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"that ' s wrong .","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"Lots of people are going to end up not buying those plans .","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"Mainly it ' s going to be an attractive place for people","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"who have existing health problems .","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"It ' s going to become essentially a program for relatively less healthy people . \"","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"Mr. Howard predicted","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"the trend will create more problems for the program , financial and political , in 2014","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"as congressional mid-term elections near .","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"\" If the picture doesn ' t improve","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"in terms","depth":15},{"id":152,"text":"of getting these young and healthy people to enroll","depth":15},{"id":153,"text":"and it stays skewed ,","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"you ' re looking at a cycle","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"where we ' re going to have more expensive rate increases for 2015 , \"","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"Mr. Howard said .","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"\" The government can push back","depth":15},{"id":158,"text":"[ against insurers ]","depth":15},{"id":159,"text":"and say","depth":15},{"id":160,"text":"the rates need to be lower ,","depth":15},{"id":161,"text":"but the insurers can say","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"' We ' ll walk. '","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"That ' s the real tension here . \"","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"As this happens ,","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"the premiums for everybody in the system then have to increase ,","depth":15},{"id":166,"text":"which makes buying insurance an even less rational act for a healthy person ,","depth":16},{"id":167,"text":"which means even fewer will sign up , and on and on - a phenomenon","depth":17},{"id":168,"text":"analysts of insurance markets refer to as the \" death spiral . \" \" The expectation was that there would be a big pool of really healthy people","depth":18},{"id":169,"text":"offsetting a relatively smaller pool of more expensive patients .","depth":18},{"id":170,"text":"If that doesn ' t play out ,","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"then the exchanges are looking at a problem in terms of affordability , a very serious problem , \"","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"Mr. Howard said .","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"While the Obama administration is saying","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"the website is getting better ,","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"the problems might also be preventing younger , healthier consumers from finding out how truly expensive their coverage would be .","depth":7},{"id":176,"text":"\" Right now , people haven ' t been able to really shop effectively , \"","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"Mr. Howard said .","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"\" A lot of these plans are going to be very narrow networks","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"and come with high deductibles .","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"Except for a few states you can purchase a plan","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"and not really understand what kind of physician and hospital coverage you ' re going to get .","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"And then I would expect lots of stories to start popping up after January","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"when people start to use the coverage","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"and hearing complaints","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"that they can ' t see the doctor","depth":12},{"id":186,"text":"they want . \"","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"Administration officials say","depth":3},{"id":188,"text":"the website should be able to handle 50,000 users simultaneously by Friday ,","depth":5},{"id":189,"text":"citing steady improvement in the speed of the site .","depth":5},{"id":190,"text":"By last week , the average load time for the website ' s pages was less than one second , down from October ' s time of eight seconds ,","depth":5},{"id":191,"text":"according to the Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services .","depth":5},{"id":192,"text":"Jeffrey Zients ,","depth":6},{"id":193,"text":"who was tapped by Mr. Obama","depth":7},{"id":194,"text":"to troubleshoot the problems with the website ,","depth":7},{"id":195,"text":"has warned","depth":5},{"id":196,"text":"that Saturday ' s deadline will not be \" a magic moment \" for the site .","depth":4},{"id":197,"text":"Instead , he said","depth":4},{"id":198,"text":"it will continue to make steady improvement .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":397,"left":385,"right":396,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":385,"left":223,"right":384,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":219,"right":222,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":214,"right":218,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":214,"left":211,"right":213,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":211,"left":202,"right":210,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":0,"right":201,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":201,"left":1,"right":200,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":200,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":207,"right":209,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":203,"right":206,"relation":"joint"